reviewText: The Cover Alone Is Worth This Dvd. Alittle More Tane To Gawk At. What A Body!!! I Dont Say She Has Got The Accolades Say Like Shannon Tweed. But She Showa A Lot More Skin. Ill Get Any Dvd That Tane Stars In.  Michael Jacobsen

I think movies and TV shows pretty much speak for themselves. If you are searching for this movie/show, you must be considering buying it. I purchased this for my electronic library because I did not feel the need to have the media. I am very happy with the fact that I can go to my library from my phone or tablet whenever I want to and watch this. It is also handy to be able to access it on my home theatre system you finish one and then go to the next; it avoids having to run up and down the stairs switching out DVDs .
there is nothing "x" rated about this! very poor acting. I've seen much better on premium cable like HBO and Showtime. the "nurses" looked pretty good but there is nothing explicit to be rated "x".
